*Prošlo* leto nisam bio na more. (I wasn't at the sea last year.)

Prošlog meseca smo posetili staru zgradu. (We visited an old building last month.)

*Prošla* nedelja bila je veoma uzbudljiva. (The last week was very exciting.)

*Prošli* put smo proveli dan na igralištu. (We spent a day at the playground last time.)

*Prošli* put kad sam bila u Londonu, bilo je veoma interesantno. (Last time when I was in London, it was very interesting.)